snippet.textDisplay: Thank you, Murphys, and everyone who helped them make Streaming Up From Boston happen. Good luck be with you. You go your way; I'll go mine. So until the next time, it's farewell and not goodbye!

My band normally practices on Tuesday nights, but we weren't able to this week because some were sick (just seasonal allergies, no Corona LoL).
So instead, my husband and I stayed in and watched Boondock Saints. I woke up the next day and watched this amazing live concert to continue in the spirit of my ancestors, and celebrate my Irish heritage. This was great. Thanks, brothers, for doing this concert! I know it meant a lot to many of us!
